Look at https://github.com/lefoyer/rememberme

Installing rememberme plugin
---------------------------------------

You need roundcube > 0.9 installed.

1. Download the latest version it to the roundcube plugins dir :

    mkdir <path_to_roundcube>/plugins/rememberme

    cd <path_to_roundcube>/plugins/rememberme

    git clone https://github.com/lefoyer/rememberme.git .

2. Add "rememberme" to the plugins list in <path_to_roundcube>/config/main.inc.php, for example :

    $rcmail_config['plugins'] = array('rememberme',);

It works :)


Configuration
-------------

You can customize some settings :

    copy config.inc.php.dist to config.inc.php
    edit config.inc.php as you fancy
